title: Raquex Badminton Shuttlecocks - Yellow/White, Tube of 6 - All Natural Cork Shuttlecocks, Nylon Feathers - Three Speed Options – Indoor Outdoor Durable Badminton Shuttles
features: DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - Raquex Shuttlecocks come in a tube of 6 and are built to last, featuring a composite cork ball head and a robust nylon shuttle frame. The synthetic nylon feathers provide exceptional durability, ensuring longevity and consistent performance during every game.

PREMIUM, ALL NATURAL CORK HEAD - Unlike cheaper alternatives, Raquex badminton shuttlecocks boast a natural cork ball head. This premium feature enhances the flight and feel of each shot, providing players with a superior playing experience and increased control over their game.

BALANCED WEIGHT, OPTIONAL SPEEDS – Weighing just 5.3g each, and three speed options: 77 Medium, 78 Fast, 79 Very fast. Raquex’s nylon shuttlecocks strike the perfect balance between agility and stability, contributing to a consistent and reliable flight, perfect for players of all skill levels, including beginners.

VERSATILE INDOOR OUTDOOR PLAY - Whether you're practising indoors, training on the badminton court, engaging in school sports, or enjoying recreational badminton play outdoors, Raquex badminton shuttlecocks are suitable for various playing environments.

UK SPORTS BRAND – Raquex is a UK sports brand that specialises in racquet sports and offers premium quality sports products and gift sets for both professional athletes and those who enjoy sports as a leisurely pastime or outdoor activity. All Raquex products are designed and stocked in the UK.
description: Product Description Badminton Shuttlecocks Elevate your badminton game with Raquex nylon feathered shuttlecocks, the perfect blend of durability and performance for your badminton game. Available in classic white or vibrant yellow shuttlecocks, each tube contains six feather shuttles featuring a natural cork ball head. Our own durable nylon feathers ensure superior durability.
